<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>爆料台 - ${site.name}</title>
<meta http-equiv="keywords" content="${site.keywords!}"/>
<meta http-equiv="description" content="${site.description!}"/>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/${res}/css/blt.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/${res}/css/public_all.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/${res}/css/global.css" />
<script type="text/javascript" src="/${res}/js/dc/settitle.js"></script>

<script src="${resSys}/jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="${resSys}/front.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>

<body>

[#include "../include/header2.html"/]


<!--nav 开始-->
[#include "../include/navi.html"/]

<!--nav 开始-->
<div style=" clear:both;"></div>

<!--内容 开始-->
<div class="box mt10">
    <div class="map"><img src="/${res}/images/home.png" width="20" height="18"><a href="/">首页</a> >  <a href="${base}/baoliao.jspx">爆料台</a> </div>
    <div style=" clear:both;"></div>
    <div class="details">
                    <div class="article_title">${baoliao.title!}</div>
                    <div class="time">${baoliao.createTime?string('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm')}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;浏览[#if baoliao.readCount ??](${baoliao.readCount})[#else](0)[/#if] 
                         &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:red;">[#if baoliao.state ??][#if baoliao.state == 0]爆料待处理[/#if][#if baoliao.state == 1]爆料处理中[/#if][#if baoliao.state == 2]爆料已解决[/#if][#else]爆料待处理[/#if] </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="article">    
                                [#if baoliao.pictures?size gt 0]
                                [#list baoliao.pictures as pic]
                                <center><img src="${pic.imgPath!}" width="350" height="300"></center>
                                [/#list]
                                [/#if]              
                             <p>${baoliao.content!}</p>
                             [#include "../content/inc_share.html"/]
                            <div style=" clear:both;"></div>
                            [#if baoliao.reply??]
                            <div class="progress">
                                    <h6>爆料进度回复</h6>
                                    <div class="progress_cont">
                                        <h1>[#if baoliao.replyTime??]${baoliao.replyTime?string('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm')}[/#if]</h1>
                                        <h2>${baoliao.reply!}</h2>
                                        <h3>东楚网</h3>
                                    </div>   
                            </div>  
                            [/#if]                      
                     </div> 
                     <div class="send_mess">我要评论 <span style="float:right;"><a href="${base}/baoliaocommt.jspx?baoliaoId=${baoliao.id}" target="_blank">已有[#if baoliao.commtCount??]${baoliao.commtCount}[#else]0[/#if]条评论</a></span></div>
                     [#include "bl_comment_input.html"/]
                     [#include "bl_comment_list.html"/]
                     

  </div>
    
[#include "bl_right.html"/]
    

           
</div>
<!--内容 end-->

<!--尾部 开始-->
<div style=" clear:both;"></div>
